    <Folder>
      <name>不吃海鮮的可以來這裡</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>White Sands Beach House</name>
        <description>金巴蘭海鮮餐廳推薦：https://gobaligo.id/go/jimbaran-seafood-recommend</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.1637649,-8.7812252,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Waroeng Kampoeng</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5dcuZutI5XbjapLnHDzHuAhdhfOGQXLwto02ttpumSCm8GrIDygq_vnpxAaKKaglyXkasGqeCTRFY4pD_XrD9G6H9Pp78zH_pBnbnrWaaVUSuNTQMjHu5tyO44mDJEX16F7Bn-IppfYimyw8a2Kg8V3o3NUdSXux3XCV4xDTftHZt-jYB5quHJZHc-rZcGyt5yplxi4Vll2CMR_czRMhQHAgyEX5yeNxXAwJKQMajN4ilt8HjKA55lh74?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>（李秋雄提供）位於金巴蘭附近的這家餐廳,  我們在2016年第一次造訪峇里島時, 第一個晚餐, 第一個食物, 就是帶我們來這家餐廳, 一吃就愛上了, 之後2018跟2023再次來峇里島, 一定都會來這裡用餐<br><br>這家的沙嗲個人覺得很厲害, 濃濃的醬香味, 搭配上炭烤過的雞肉沙嗲, OMG!! 只能說是目前心中的第一名, 其他菜色像是炒麵, 糖醋魚, 烤蛤蜊, 炸蝦, 炒青菜, 都很有水準, 我們一行5人, 加上酒水, 吃了大概1500台幣<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X76JQF4jwZku660Q5w0v1aUqjZaR6iVP6PZUT8LXi1vjCgImmWg-Zr29bTe--pXvB0l2C0A4MuDwqgZgDA1d5q_tFsl8RGJxZmrH7fJaDKJDJTydzCh2RPfNLOltk5xK6b8_rulkF8aLzMV0Yxal1Xskh0QXSbr75rVMToPaA7tiOeYEazgrF7JKExAGPUwkDg2VAkHmZsbhMf6Pla6qW9z3BHttKzmm6at_X6vKDxaqRyJtnfBHxqr1uk?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5dcuZutI5XbjapLnHDzHuAhdhfOGQXLwto02ttpumSCm8GrIDygq_vnpxAaKKaglyXkasGqeCTRFY4pD_XrD9G6H9Pp78zH_pBnbnrWaaVUSuNTQMjHu5tyO44mDJEX16F7Bn-IppfYimyw8a2Kg8V3o3NUdSXux3XCV4xDTftHZt-jYB5quHJZHc-rZcGyt5yplxi4Vll2CMR_czRMhQHAgyEX5yeNxXAwJKQMajN4ilt8HjKA55lh74?authuser=0&fife=s16383 https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X76JQF4jwZku660Q5w0v1aUqjZaR6iVP6PZUT8LXi1vjCgImmWg-Zr29bTe--pXvB0l2C0A4MuDwqgZgDA1d5q_tFsl8RGJxZmrH7fJaDKJDJTydzCh2RPfNLOltk5xK6b8_rulkF8aLzMV0Yxal1Xskh0QXSbr75rVMToPaA7tiOeYEazgrF7JKExAGPUwkDg2VAkHmZsbhMf6Pla6qW9z3BHttKzmm6at_X6vKDxaqRyJtnfBHxqr1uk?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.1811695,-8.7826701,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
